{"id":539581,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/09/努力加餐饭-陈小花：听说最近都不让去杭州，于/","date":"2016-09-04T01:05:25Z","modified":"2016-09-04T01:07:55Z","title":"努力加餐饭 | 听说最近都不让去杭州，于是我亲自试了一下","content":"<p>作者：陈小花</p>\n<p>昨天中午吃午饭的时候，我的丈夫郑重其事的对我说：<strong>因为G20的缘故，最近杭州已经全面戒严了，不许随便进入，而且路边的小店都已经关闭了。整个杭州现在就是一个舞台，路上的行人都是军人扮演的，而且长的都很帅。</strong></p>\n<p>深夜时分，我躺在床上辗转反侧，想到白天他对我说的话，内心久久不能平息。</p>\n<p>我决定要买第二天一大早的火车从上海去杭州亲眼看一看——遇到这么精彩的历史事件、面对人生仅有一次的杭州大舞台，我不能错过！</p>\n<p>于是今天早晨，我购买了从上海虹桥火车站去往杭州东站的高铁票，决意一探究竟。我此行主要是为了搞清楚三件事情：</p>\n<ol class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n<li><strong>杭州到底是不是禁止进入？</strong></li>\n<li><strong>路边的小店是不是都关闭了？</strong></li>\n<li><strong>路上的行人是不是军人扮演的？</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>我穿好衣服，带好身份证，临走前先去看了一下我那一大早就下楼去玩耍的宝宝。</p>\n<p>我对保姆阿姨说：“我去杭州了，你在家里好好带宝宝。”她立刻使用了她的万能金句“嗯。”，然后一脸懵逼——只有我的儿子最理解我，他的表情好像在说我妈就是个逗逼。</p>\n<p>（不要问我为什么1岁的孩子会长得这么高，也不要问我为什么他会玩滑板车。我也是第一次养孩子，也不知道这是不是属于正常现象。）</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539582\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.49.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.49.18\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.49.18.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.49.18-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>我先是来到了上海虹桥火车站。一切指征正常，连上海的天空都占了G20的光，一片蔚蓝。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539583\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.04.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.50.04\" width=\"572\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.04.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.04-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>通过火车站大门处的安检后，现在增设了【第二道安检】。安检处分为“开往北方的列车”和“开往南方的列车”两个入口。我一不去哈尔滨，二不去海南岛，一时之间有点搞不清楚杭州到底是在南还是在北……</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539584\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.50.35\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.35.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.50.35-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>由于“开往北方的车辆”免于第二次安检可以走快速通道，而“开往南方的车辆”则必须进行实名制第二次安检，所以我果断选择了<strong>比较复杂</strong>的道路。事实证明我是对的。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539585\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.05.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.51.05\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.05.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.05-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>高铁一路顺畅，一小时之后妥妥的到达了杭州东站。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539586\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.38.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.51.38\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.38.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.51.38-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>出站之后我一路非常激动，抱着看热闹不怕事大的心态，十分期待有警察能够把我拦住，然后把我遣返至上海——然而并没有，一切安泰。不过出口的地方又增设了一道安检。我靠，出站也要安检我倒是第一次遇到。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539587\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.52.05.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.52.05\" width=\"571\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.52.05.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.52.05-300x226.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>G20峰会的志愿者在火车站服务，右边举高牌的这一位内心好像很激动。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539588\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.27.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.53.27\" width=\"571\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.27.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.27-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>我又怀着忐忑的心情走进地铁站，准备乘地铁去杭州最著名的西湖。刚到地铁站看到这片景象的时候，我承认，我有一点点方。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539589\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.53.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.53.53\" width=\"571\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.53.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.53.53-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>因为我的丈夫说过，杭州的市民都是由军人扮演的，所以我在地铁上十分仔细的观察来往的乘客。你看这对小夫妻，演的多逼真。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539590\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.21.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.54.21\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.21.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.21-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>出了地铁，我兴高采烈的奔向西湖。迎面遇到一辆神秘的白色车牌的面包车，一位军人叔叔从车上走下来，与另一位看上去深藏不漏的重要人士亲切握手。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539591\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.51.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.54.51\" width=\"568\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.51.png 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.54.51-300x226.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></p>\n<p>我走啊走，一会儿就走到了西湖的入口处——兴奋的心情戛然而止。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539592\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.19.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.55.19\" width=\"571\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.19.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.19-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>我很天真的，我准备在门口排队等候，等人少的时候再进去。然后我在旁边绕来绕去，看到另一个入口写着这样的牌子。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539593\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.46.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.55.46\" width=\"573\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.46.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.55.46-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>讲真？不是说人数已饱和的吗？停止对外开放人数究竟是怎么饱和的呢？能不能不要欺负外地人，说点实话好吗？</p>\n<p>于是我又想到了我丈夫曾经语重心长对我说的话：“路边的小店都已经关闭了。”</p>\n<p>我抬头向四周一看，是这样的：</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539594\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.11.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.56.11\" width=\"572\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.11.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.11-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>这样的：</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539595\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.56.35\" width=\"572\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.35.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.35-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>因为“内部调整”暂停营业？这！么！巧！</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539596\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.58.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.56.58\" width=\"570\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.58.png 570w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.56.58-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" /></p>\n<p>店铺升级？你确定你真的要升级？</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539597\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.24.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.57.24\" width=\"573\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.24.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.24-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>内部设施改造？</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539598\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.47.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.57.47\" width=\"571\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.47.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.57.47-300x226.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>对面整个一栋楼都是关闭的，告示上写的什么太远了我看不清。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539599\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.11.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.58.11\" width=\"573\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.11.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.11-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>“喜迎G20全体员工放假”……终于找到一家说实话的了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539600\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.36.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.58.36\" width=\"570\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.36.png 570w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.58.36-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" /></p>\n<p>不过也有一些小店是开门营业的，粗略估计，大约每五家店铺中有一家营业。在营业的店铺中，规模和经营内容都没有什么规律性，好像比较随机。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539601\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.15.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.59.15\" width=\"571\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.15.png 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.15-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></p>\n<p>公交车还在运行中，但是公交车站的便民自行车，不知道为什么一辆都没有了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539602\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.40.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午5.59.40\" width=\"573\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.40.png 573w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午5.59.40-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" /></p>\n<p>地铁过道中也有持枪的警察随机检查身份证。我站在边上偷偷观察了好久，一般是长的不太好的容易被抽查到，像我这种动机不纯的人，反而没有被检查。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539603\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.00.05.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午6.00.05\" width=\"570\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.00.05.png 570w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.00.05-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" /></p>\n<p>我折来折去，又折到西湖的入口处，通过嘘寒问暖并送上一杯冰镇金桔柠檬茶的方式与一位保安大叔建立了速成型的友谊。</p>\n<p>我问他有没有其他的小路可以进入西湖景区？他说24小时都有人站岗的，是没法进去的。我觉得他说的应该是真话，因为他喝了一大口金桔柠檬茶。</p>\n<p>（没有保安大叔的照片，这是机密）</p>\n<p>兜兜转转之后，我百般无奈，只好打道回沪。我特地挑选了与来时不一样的火车站（杭州城站）上车，车站内也是一片祥和气氛。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539604\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.01.17.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午6.01.17\" width=\"572\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.01.17.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.01.17-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>但是等我登上月台、走进车厢的时候，看见了如此空旷的包厢。我不得不承认，我当时还是稍微有一点方。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539605\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.02.31.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午6.02.31\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.02.31.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.02.31-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>终于又回到上海了，这拥挤的人山人海、人海人山、山山海海、海海山山又重新让我获得了现实世界的安全感。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539606\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.02.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午6.03.02\" width=\"572\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.02.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.02-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n<p>总结此次亲历杭州大舞台的经历，用事实告诉大家三件事：</p>\n<ol class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n<li><strong>G20期间杭州是可以进出的，不过西湖和其他重要景点是关闭的。</strong></li>\n<li><strong>路边的小店确实都关闭了。</strong></li>\n<li><strong>路上的行人大多数还是真正的行人，看图就知道了，也没有什么长的特别帅的。</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>最后奉上一张本文作者在杭州地铁上喜不自禁的自拍。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-539607\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.22.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-09-03 at 下午6.03.22\" width=\"572\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.22.png 572w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/Screen-Shot-2016-09-03-at-下午6.03.22-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[19851,30689,20588,31638,10452,10265,30680]}